  "Description": {
    "English": "A unique and exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">starship</span>, commemorating completion of the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Adrift</span> expedition.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘独一无二的专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，用于纪念你完成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">漂泊</span>远征。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘獨一無二的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，用以紀念<span class=\"name name-stellar\">漂泊</span>探險的完成。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，使用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
